## 📌 2. Ethereum Gas Fee Optimization Dashboard  

**Tools:** Power BI | SQL | Excel  

### 🔍 Business Problem  
Ethereum users often overpay transaction fees due to lack of visibility into gas fee trends.  

### 📊 Solution  
Built an interactive dashboard to analyze historical gas fees and identify optimal transaction times.  

### ⚙️ Process  
- Extracted gas fee data from blockchain APIs  
- Transformed and modeled data in SQL  
- Designed interactive Power BI dashboard  
- Created time-based trend analysis  

### 📈 Key Insights  
- Identified peak and off-peak transaction periods  
- Highlighted daily and weekly gas fee patterns  
- Detected anomalies in transaction costs  

### 💡 Business Value  
- Helps users minimize transaction costs  
- Provides actionable insights for optimal transaction timing  
- Improves cost efficiency for frequent traders  

